":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bb765ec38659915bb3669966a5a3c5607fbea2e5","tid":878383,"uid":114027,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:34:58.000Z","msg":"老豆老母做ngo做到住跑馬地<br />\n呢單新聞算唔算透露左d所謂的ngo有幾腐敗？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"NGO都有醫生律師會計師<br />\n你知唔知咩叫NGO<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}